{"tid":1161783,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我話知你'97 其實駛乜驚到求神又拜佛","createTime":"2019-05-19T12:09:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-24T12:27:18.000Z","uid":52215,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c11e1fb1d2cb98372e6b6924f4e5123f4b66e492","tid":1161783,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T12:09:17.000Z","msg":"我話知你'97 其實駛乜驚到求神又拜佛(大喊十)<br />\n已經胃酸過多夾風濕(重有久咳) 成日閉翳實聽吃弗得(重有執笠)<br />\n未有耐到'97 起枝筆數 二千零廿八日(駛乜急) 已經預冇法走得甩<br />\n(又冇 Short Cut) 移民外國亦系聽糟質 咪匿 屋企速速Call機<br />\nCall班知己 睇番出無厘頭攪笑戲 卡拉OK「堆」樽拔蘭地<br />\nHigh High 高聲亂唱再去旺角打機 買份八卦雜誌睇<br />\n大姐楣 「及」 邊個整容後揚 威選美 明日懶鬼理 最緊要依家<br />\nHappy 話知佢死 我話知你'97 其實香港適應力強未嚇窒(好煉得)<br />\n斷估或者到 '97(又變 乜) 繁榮盛世度度有金執 斷估或者到<br />\n'97(實刮多筆) 人人暴發 My friend, good luck<br />\n(Good luck, good luck, God bless 1997 阿陀侘佛"},{"pid":"22fdce7f137e312bd48f3a0eaaae9820cfd726a3","tid":1161783,"uid":37528,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T12:10:21.000Z","msg":"香港是我家 一顆不變心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n轉頭就去移民"},{"pid":"385286915108327c4297c3431f85174c2d24447a","tid":1161783,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T12:11:44.000Z","msg":"許冠傑真係我偶像"},{"pid":"747c9a34c8eee25580124f93affd3334b6af77a4","tid":1161783,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22fdce7f137e312bd48f3a0eaaae9820cfd726a3","tid":1161783,"uid":37528,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T12:10:21.000Z","msg":"香港是我家 一顆不變心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n轉頭就去移民"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T12:12:53.000Z","msg":"有冇邊單新聞證明過許冠傑移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3adeca998848cc20ff4ce6fafa9ec6039e6226ae","tid":1161783,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score